values ('Almond Fruit Roll Cake', 20, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474243/pexels-photo-7474243.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'This decadent roll cake is the perfect dessert to complement a beautiful bouquet of flowers (or to be enjoyed on its own). The fruits include blueberries, strawberries, raspberries, and slices of lemon for a bright lift. Then it is topped with our freshly made whipped cream and slivers of almonds. A true delight!', 2),
('Blushing in Pink', 30, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/931180/pexels-photo-931180.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Best seller - Brighten up that special day with this luxurious bouquet arranged by our artisan florists. The stems include carnations, roses, and hydrangeas. This charming arrangement will certainly please.', 1),
('Pink Macarons with Carnations', 24, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474291/pexels-photo-7474291.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'By the dozen, these macarons are beautifully packaged in a box complemented with florets of pink carnations. The macarons are filled with a rose-flavored filling, making a dessert so stunning that it is almost too pretty to eat.', 2),
('Buncha Lavender', 15, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/171259/pexels-photo-171259.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Per bunch, each about 12-15 inches long and containing around 100-150 individual lavender stems. Perfect to add some country-chic flair to your room or to send an aromatic gift to your loved one. Basket not included.', 1),
('Chocolate Fruit Cupcakes', 36, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7646676/pexels-photo-7646676.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'By the dozen, these cupcakes are delivered in a temperature-controlled package. The fruits include blueberries, strawberries, blackberries, and a slice of orange for a bright lift. Topped with our freshly made chocolate cream and a square of 60% cacao dark chocolate.', 2),
('Carnation Carnival', 25, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2879824/pexels-photo-2879824.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Is there someone in your life that you are wild about? Express your affections by gifting this beautiful bouquet! The stems include carnations, roses, and lilies. This wildly gorgeous arrangement will certain wow that special someone.', 1),
('Meringue Cookies with Carnations', 15, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474332/pexels-photo-7474332.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Each order contains five meringue cookies with eight florets of pink carnations. A beautiful addition to any occasion and a certain way to thrill your recipient.', 2),
('Feeling Frilly', 20, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7876485/pexels-photo-7876485.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Whether the occasion is a birthday, a “get well”, or just because, this fun bouquet will brighten up any day. The stems include a large pink camellia, roses, eucalyptus leaves, and English daisies. A fun way to show how much you care.', 1),
('Berry Cupcakes with English Daisies', 36, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/4099124/pexels-photo-4099124.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'By the dozen, these cupcakes are delivered in a temperature-controlled package. The fruits include blackberries, raspberries, and a slice of orange for a bright lift. Topped with our freshly made lemon cream.', 2),
('Hi Daisy', 18, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/4022213/pexels-photo-4022213.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'This pretty bouquet includes pink daisies, white daisies, and tulips. A perfect way to show your care to someone or to just brighten up the room. A great choice for any occasion.', 1),
('Lavender Macarons', 28, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474241/pexels-photo-7474241.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'By the dozen, these macarons are beautifully packaged in a box complemented with a bunch of lavender. The macarons are filled with a lavender-flavored filling and come with lilac and teal-colored biscuits, lightly dusted with gold dust. A heavenly treat that will guarantee smiles.', 2),
('Just Rosy', 60, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/931154/pexels-photo-931154.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Best seller - A stunning array of roses in a variety of colors, including peach, yellow and pink. Adorned with eucalyptus and silver dollar leaves, this arrangement will not disappoint. Arrives in a grey vessel.', 1),
('Chocolate Donuts with Pansies', 15, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474262/pexels-photo-7474262.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Each order contains six chocolate-frosted donuts adorned with six violet pansies. Donuts are topped with sprinkles, peanuts, and dehydrated rose petals, creating a dessert that is as dazzling as it is decadent.', 2),
('Pink and Purple Macarons', 22, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474228/pexels-photo-7474228.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'By the dozen, these macarons are garnished with vanilla icing and heart sprinkles. The macarons are filled with a mocha-flavored filling. A perfect dessert for any occasion.', 2),
('Purple Lush', 18, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/6341497/pexels-photo-6341497.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Brighten up any room with the beautiful simplicity of purple lilacs. A wonderful option to brighten up any day.', 1),
('Strawberry Macarons', 14, 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/7474138/pexels-photo-7474138.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940', 'Each order contains six strawberry-shaped macarons filled with strawberry-flavored filling. A delightful addition to a bouquet of flowers for any occasion.', 2),
